content: conache: Merged two significant PRs this month, with the most substantial being #1955 "feat: Add Allora plugin" which added over 51k lines and removed 42k lines. Also merged PR #2707 to update the Allora SDK version, collectively modifying 1,298 files across 8 commits. Activity was sporadic, occurring on only 4 days this month, with changes primarily focused on code and configuration files.
